{"tid":2273191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MI係咪BLOCK左香港IP唔俾查死人票","createTime":"2020-11-05T14:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T14:20:53.000Z","uid":58841,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eb04ca3559ffa367fe29a8b3d63e7a23ee4a2ed0","tid":2273191,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"是咁既<br />\n頭先有個巴打POST話好多人瑞投票 個陣仲查到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2272765/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2272765/page/1</a><br />\n而家諗住俾錢睇死亡登記冊chok資料出黎發現個網上唔到<br />\n我有搵返條LINK出處的確係官方叫人去track<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.michigan.gov/sos/0,4670,7-127-1633_8716_8728-21037--,00.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.michigan.gov%2Fsos%2F0%2C4670%2C7-127-1633_8716_8728-21037--%2C00.html&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=350e47ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.michigan.gov/sos/0,4670,7-127-1633_8716_8728-21037--,00.html</a><br />\n<em>All registered voters are eligible to vote by mail<br />\nDue to the passage of the statewide ballot proposal 18-3, all eligible and registered voters in Michigan may now request an absent voter ballot without providing a reason.<br />\nCheck your voter registration at Michigan Voter Information Center <a href=\"http://Michigan.gov/Vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMichigan.gov%2FVote&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=ede10587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Michigan.gov/Vote</a></em><br />\n<a href=\"https://mvic.sos.state.mi.us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmvic.sos.state.mi.us%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8vilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=64c56e41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mvic.sos.state.mi.us/</a><br />\n然後就上唔到了<br />\n開左NORD VPN先望到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想知淨係我個IP有問題定佢真係靜靜雞BLOCK香港IP<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706a49d7b670107807e053b58f6ecf3f9c8ee0a3","tid":2273191,"uid":308915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"試下開美國VPN睇下上唔上到"},{"pid":"84f8485e6e777de51ffd5e59761e59397488f138","tid":2273191,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"706a49d7b670107807e053b58f6ecf3f9c8ee0a3","tid":2273191,"uid":308915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"試下開美國VPN睇下上唔上到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"美國同台灣VPN係上到<br />\n之後熄左VPN就上唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左求證我想睇埋其他連登仔有冇相同情況出現"},{"pid":"3002e53438ce101ff495546b3e4fb83f17838cd5","tid":2273191,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"我開唔開香港vpn都上到喎"},{"pid":"58ffadf26d2fb7a1b2f4fc6b25e6a5068c4b36d6","tid":2273191,"uid":214679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"直接開到"},{"pid":"ceea819142d1013ca387e54d91b6e8e19c41d06c","tid":2273191,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:20:53.000Z","msg":"大概係我問題<br />\n一陣再試"}]}